node.text:
5 fabs for your next lower body workout!
(Leggings and top: @one0one_101)

Either you do it as a circuit 4 times, or as a routine:
1️⃣10 repetitions per leg / 4 sets
2️⃣15 repetitions / 4 sets
3️⃣8 repetitions per leg / 4 sets
4️⃣15 repetitions / 3 sets
5️⃣10 repetitions / 3 sets

Squat today, smile tomorrow my ladies!
You got this!

node.text:
(Forgive our Spanglish) -A circuit to give those abs exactly what they need (when it comes to working out)
I would suggest you do this circuit 4 times.... if you run out of power after 3 times, it's all good... maybe next time🤷🏼‍♀️🥰
Can be done as routine too (4 sets per exercise)
Here we go:

1️⃣ 10 repetitions
2️⃣ 15 repetitions
3️⃣ 30 kicks (15 kicks per side)
4️⃣A: 10 reps, followed by
4️⃣B: 6 reps

-Outfit @one0one_101 🥰
-Train with me & @Jimmy_Lewin on @Fitplan_App (tambien en ESPAÑOL!!)
-Video by @MaiTieProductions at @MiamiStrongGym

node.text:
No matter if you are getting rid of flabby overarms, or building triceps in general, the basic is the same: the "pushing away" movement is the way to go. Sometime heavy with few reps, sometimes light with a lot of reps. Keep changing your workouts constantly for best results.

Here I have a program for you to get an excellent triceps workout.
Today you can do this as a routine (4 sets), and next triceps day do this as a circuit (if the gym is not too crowded), and do the circuit 4 times.

Wearing @one0one_101 summer workout wear🥰
-Need more routines, circuits and full workout programs? Try any of my plans on the app FITPLAN (start for free via my website, link in bio). Tambien en ESPANOL!!

A quite basic back work out routine for the gym. But hey! This is Miami🍾😜
-You better train that back, babe!💁🏼‍♀️ Why? Well… a well developed back will pull your shoulders backwards. And that means? In a few words it will:
1️⃣make your posture WAY better, and 2️⃣eliminate (certain) back issues.

Try this basic, but effective, back workout next time you go to the gym.

node.text:
so I'm in THAT mood😬✌🏻and leg day it is🏋🏼‍♀️🥳
Here's a breakdown of the routine:
1️⃣Hamstring curl: 15 reps per hamstring / 5 sets
2️⃣Sumo squats: 15 reps / 4 sets
3️⃣Back kicks: 15 kicks per leg / 4 sets
4️⃣Calf press: 25 reps / 6-7 sets
(What no one knew about me: as a child, I took arabic dance classes. I'm a bit rusty, but I still like it)

node.text:
-

Estos solo son algunos momentos de nuestras vidas. Cuantas memorias, viajes, anécdotas, y sueños juntos y los que nos faltan por cumplir. 
-
Todo ha sido perfecto hasta hoy, gracias por haber llegado a mi vida, me has enseñado tanto y  sigo aprendiendo a tu lado. 
-
No cambiaría absolutamente nada de lo que hemos vivido.  Solo le pido a Dios  que te de vida, salud  y que te mantenga con esa hermosa energía de niño que tienes, para que sigamos disfrutando y coleccionando momentos juntos.
-
Que tu corazón no deje nunca de latir nunca ❤️, para que me sigas amando tanto como yo te amo a ti.
-
Aprovecho para notificarles a ustedes familia que ya tenemos fecha de la Cirugía del corazón  de mi Jimmy. Marzo / 01 / 2021 
Les pido de corazón que me ayuden a orar para que todo salga bien 🙏🏻
-
Michelle 

Voz: @emmahewittofficial

This year, I’m choosing STRONG Nation as my go-to HIIT workout. 💪Their custom music matches every move perfectly to the beat, so I stop counting reps! I can really feel the difference, the music motivates me to keep pushing past my limits and the results come with it🔥
You can try the program for FREE with their new 10-minute demo: @wearestrongnation

node.text:
-Yes mami, these were posted on my Stories yesterday (wearing @one0one_101), but you ladies blew my inbox into pieces with all requests to post these videos “normally" so they won't disappear... so here they are!
This can be done as a workout routine, or as a circuit (4 sets. Or 5, if you still got the power to do it)😬

1️⃣15 repetitions per leg 
2️⃣12 repetitions per leg
3️⃣15 repetitions
4️⃣12 repetitions 
5️⃣20 repetitions

Just keep it up, girls! If you need more home workouts, I have a 60 day program for you on the app Fitplan. Download it for free from my website (link in bio), TAMBIÉN EN ESPAÑOL!

Squat today, smile tomorrow my ladies!
You got this!

node.text:
(Forgive our Spanglish) -A circuit to give those abs exactly what they need (when it comes to working out)
I would suggest you do this circuit 4 times.... if you run out of power after 3 times, it's all good... maybe next time🤷🏼‍♀️🥰
Can be done as routine too (4 sets per exercise)
Here we go:

1️⃣ 10 repetitions
2️⃣ 15 repetitions
3️⃣ 30 kicks (15 kicks per side)
4️⃣A: 10 reps, followed by
4️⃣B: 6 reps

-Outfit @one0one_101 🥰
-Train with me & @Jimmy_Lewin on @Fitplan_App (tambien en ESPAÑOL!!)
-Video by @MaiTieProductions at @MiamiStrongGym

No matter if you are getting rid of flabby overarms, or building triceps in general, the basic is the same: the "pushing away" movement is the way to go. Sometime heavy with few reps, sometimes light with a lot of reps. Keep changing your workouts constantly for best results.

Here I have a program for you to get an excellent triceps workout.
Today you can do this as a routine (4 sets), and next triceps day do this as a circuit (if the gym is not too crowded), and do the circuit 4 times.

Wearing @one0one_101 summer workout wear🥰
-Need more routines, circuits and full workout programs? Try any of my plans on the app FITPLAN (start for free via my website, link in bio). Tambien en ESPANOL!!
